draft.title: SMARTYPANTS Pumpkin Picking Crew Sweatshirt - Autumn Jumper For Women Men | Cosy Watercolour Wheelbarrow Design | Seasonal Halloween Outfit | Unisex Pullover Top For Fall Harvest
draft.description:
Embrace the cosy spirit of the season with the SMARTYPANTS Pumpkin Picking Crew jumper. This sweatshirt features a beautifully detailed watercolour design of a rustic wheelbarrow brimming with autumnal gourds perfect for your next trip to the pumpkin patch or a crisp walk in the park.

Crafted for exceptional comfort and warmth its soft cotton-blend fabric makes it an essential layering piece. Whether you're buying for yourself or as a thoughtful seasonal gift this charming pullover is a wonderful way to celebrate autumn in style.

bullets: Charming Autumn Design – Celebrate the season with this beautiful watercolour wheelbarrow full of pumpkins - the perfect top for your annual pumpkin patch trip or as a thoughtful autumn gift.
Premium Cosy Fabric – Made from a soft and durable cotton blend this jumper offers superior comfort and warmth making it your go-to layer for crisp autumnal days and chilly evenings.
Easy Care Wear – This versatile pullover is designed for real life being fully machine washable for simple care while retaining its comfortable fit and soft feel wash after wash.
Vibrant Lasting Print – The detailed watercolour graphic is applied using advanced printing technology ensuring the rich autumnal colours remain bright and fade-resistant through many seasons.
Versatile Seasonal Style – Arriving ready to gift this cosy jumper is ideal for casual outings layering over outfits or simply enjoying a warm drink at home embracing the spirit of autumn.
